latestIgtvVideos.title: It’s been over a week
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It’s been over a week since you left us. 
It’s been hard for me to accept that you are not with me anymore ,Everyday I wake up looking for you, every time I cook something I call for you but then it strikes me that there is no point calling for you as you are no longer here with me . I still remember the day I met you like it was yesterday you were just a little puppy and I was a little girl, we grew up together , faced ups and downs together . Without you this house , our room feels empty , I hope wherever you are , you are happy and at peace . I will miss you and I will love you forever . 
Cheers to our happy memories ❤️
